						<li><strong>Dark Theme:</strong> Beautiful fantasy-themed dark mode easy on the eyes</li>
						<li><strong>Keyboard Shortcuts:</strong> Navigate combat faster with hotkeys</li>
						<li><strong>No Installation:</strong> Works instantly in any modern browser</li>
						<li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> All data stays on your device - nothing sent to servers</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

			<div class="bg-secondary/20 p-6 rounded-lg mt-12">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to streamline your D&D combat?</h3>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
						Try our free initiative tracker today - no sign-up required, no downloads, just start tracking.
					</p>
					<a href="/" class="inline-block bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
						Start Using Initiative Tracker
					</a>
